data.description: Need to get away and be lost from the everyday hustle and bustle, well speak no more. Enjoy this quiet 1 bedroom 2 full bath off the power grid cabin on 2.5 acres. The interior brings a cabin home feel, with a full size kitchen, entry level full size bathroom, living room, master bedroom with master bathroom, and a loft area that can give to another sleeping area or a quiet space to read. Relax in this tranquil mountain hideaway cabin as you sit on your back deck with south facing views of the mountain ridge that stare down at the North Fork Tuolumne River. Natural cool breezes that whistle through the river canyon give an inviting reason to open the windows or sit on the deck and just relax.
